-  NSMetadataUbiquitousItemPercentUploadedKey 

Global Variable# NSMetadataUbiquitousItemPercentUploadedKey

iOS 5.0+iPadOS 5.0+Mac Catalyst 13.1+macOS 10.7+tvOS 9.0+visionOS 1.0+watchOS 2.0+

```
let NSMetadataUbiquitousItemPercentUploadedKey: String
```

## [Discussion](/documentation/foundation/nsmetadataubiquitousitempercentuploadedkey#Discussion)

The value is an [`NSNumber`](/documentation/foundation/nsnumber) object that contains the percentage of the file that has already been uploaded to the cloud. The value is a double in the range `0.0` to `100.0`.
